stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> NotStarted
    NotStarted --> Validating : Start Deployment
    Validating --> BackingUp : Validation Pass
    Validating --> Failed : Validation Fail
    BackingUp --> Deploying : Backup Success
    Deploying --> RollingBack : Install Fail
    Deploying --> HealthChecking : Install Success
    HealthChecking --> Completed : Check Pass
    HealthChecking --> RollingBack : Check Fail
    RollingBack --> Failed : Rollback Done
    Completed --> [*]
    Failed --> [*]
